Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STRATEGY MEETING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STRATEGY MEETING\NJust when we thought damage\Nto the city would be inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STRATEGY MEETING\Na powerful attack pulverized\Nthat giant creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a powerful attack pulverized\Nthat giant creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying Centichoro\Ndisappeared without a trace?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe, but this is\Na feat only King could pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are incredibly lucky to\Nhave King as our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the Hero Hunter, I hear\NSilverfang failed to capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do\Nabout this, Sitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he continues to\Nhunt heroes like this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hero Association\Nwill cease to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must no longer view Garou\Nas a human, but as a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time he appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be categorized as\Nthreat level Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an emergency alert\Nmust be issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nhe's still a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could any normal person actually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stand up to our Class-S heroes\Nbarehanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the strategy's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Our" Class-S heroes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even at this stage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he is treating this{\i0}\N{\i1}as some kind of business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unexpected that Silverfang\Nfailed to finish off Garou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he did manage to\Nleave him severely injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least this means\NGarou likely won't bolster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Monster Association's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else,\Nwe can count that as a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Blast over here!\NBlast, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a top-ranker, but he's\Nnot doing anything at all, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible\Nto give Blast orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only operates\Nas a hero voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He refuses to be bound by anyone\Nand dislikes drawing attention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so even in the registry,\Nhis identity is undisclosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because we believe he's\Nworthy of this special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if humanity really needs help
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time is now!\NA monster abducted my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 24 hours since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my word.\NWe will save your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be commanding\Nthis rescue operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sekingal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just sweep in and\Ntake care of things in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we know where the hideout is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Child Emperor is working\Nat full speed on it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have surveillance robots probing\NCentichoro's underground route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the area is huge...\Nwe have three days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have two days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...\NNo sleep for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hideout is somewhere\Nin City Z's ghost town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KABOOM\NShall I just wipe it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KABOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KABOOM\NWe must tread carefully\Nsince there is a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they hadn't done that\Nthey'd have no chance against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters must be afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponents\Nare pretty formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call us here just\Nto give us that warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive Knight forcibly continued\Nthe investigation on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored our warnings and\Nentered the ghost town ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he go alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:05:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never lost a battle,\Nso he must've been confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since last night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't been able to pick up\Na signal from his transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's safe to assume that\NDrive Knight has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry up and\Nassemble your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Association gave us\Na three-day ultimatum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the other heroes\Nare ready, they will rush over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still on standby?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child is being held hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know about that,\NAtomic Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also reek of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since yesterday, I've been\Nscouring mountains and caves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking for hidden monsters and\Nslashing 'em up, left, and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately,\NI wasn't able to find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Monster Association's\Nhideout though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the Monster Association's\Nhideout is in the ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NWe know that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fighting head-on at\Nthe hideout sounds easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest we all\Nget some rest till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- I'm going to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the assault team would\Nbe made up of an elite few, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, there are\Nsome here who don't fit the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we refrain from bringing\Nour fun friends, Atomic Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like the small fry to stick\Nto fighting other small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be so bad\Nif they just die
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what if they're taken as\Nhostages or used as human shields?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a major hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that ever happens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you give them the orders\Nto commit harakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take it easy, Mr. Handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amai Mask, are you on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Those monsters\Ninterrupted my concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:07:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. My disciples are tough,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them to protect\Nthe pretty boy idol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he gets in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who still doubt\Nmy combat abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only stay in Class A because\Nit's easier to oversee everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can move up to Class S\Nat any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, let's see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply,\Nso an imbecile can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master! Keep your cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warden, you sure I can just walk\Nright out the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an extra-legal measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me remind you that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every time you've broken\Nout of prison to do hero work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's all been illegal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like how\Nthe Hero Association
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gives a guy like you\Npreferential treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just this once,\NI can't afford to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a single cat-like monster
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who turned some of the prisoners\Ninto monsters and took them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many officers who fought back\Nlost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hero out there,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,\Nboss of the prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get revenge for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them pay dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for wrecking this place\Nwhile I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knitted a sweater for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wear it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NThis will give me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mind leaving the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't focus with\Nyou all staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're pretending\Nnot to be there. Please answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm wasting\Na lot of time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've figured out\Nwhere the hideout is by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.\NWe're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to\Nlet the hostage die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By not telling you,{\i0}\N{\i1}the hostage might die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I do tell you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bring death to not only{\i0}\N{\i1}the hostage, but to all of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will make a rational choice{\i0}\N{\i1}based on justice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can join the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the state of\Nyour machine body right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has been destroyed, which\Nmonster did that to you and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monster King Orochi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was just one strike.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The arm I used to{\i0}\N{\i1}guard myself was destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the self-destruction device{\i0}\N{\i1}was disabled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not the Monster Association{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm afraid of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evil powers are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}watching for their chance to{\i0}\N{\i1}take over the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When humanity's defenses{\i0}\N{\i1}become weak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they'll strike all at once{\i0}\N{\i1}to take everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't trust anyone around you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want to enforce justice{\i0}\N{\i1}do it alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Build up your strength...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And save it for the right time,{\i0}\N{\i1}Child Emperor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Association is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as I speak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my son is trembling in fear\Nas he waits for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head over to the abandoned area\Nof City Z immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and find the Monsters' hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And rescue my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle suits you are wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are secret weapons\Nobtained from special channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance of these suits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,easily surpass the power\Nof any professional hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NARINKI PRIVATE FORCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NARINKI PRIVATE FORCE\NMake full use of your battle suits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NARINKI PRIVATE FORCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NARINKI PRIVATE FORCE\Nand exterminate\Nevery single monster you encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and exterminate\Nevery single monster you encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay whatever you name\Nfor the success fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back Waganma alive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will live in\Nluxury for generations to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure\Nit's that small building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Blizzard Bunch{\i0}\N{\i1}has been wiped out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, half of it{\i0}\N{\i1}is my sister's fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an emergency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to use this place{\i0}\N{\i1}as a branch office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of the Blizzard Bunch{\i0}\N{\i1}to hold a meeting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saita...\NWait, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor, Saitama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blizzard's here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how come the monster I raised
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,died right away\Nwith just a single hit of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Hellish Blizzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is not\Ntaking any new disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's so cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you hand me that poultice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would wind be earth's weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm at level 27\Nand you're at level 15, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're at\Nthe highest level
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Golem can't beat\NMeow-Meow types.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a weak character\Nto begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You should've\Ntold me that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This Armpit character...\N- That one's weak too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, only the cute characters\Nare strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it.\NThat just ruined it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blizzard Bunch got wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Organization is\Nextremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time\Nto be playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea\Nwhat's going on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got home a while ago and\Nwas taking a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Master said, we were\Nalso facing some tough opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you guys\Nwere the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can tell\Nfrom the way you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know King was here before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what's Silverfang\Ndoing here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought alongside them,\Nso Saitama is letting me rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little carried away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,threw my back out,\Nand now I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My knees gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Fist of Roaring Qi, Rending Air\Nafter so long took its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it must have been\Nquite a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet why?{\i0}\N{\i1}Why is this guy the same as usual?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Saitama!\NYou're acting all cool and calm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're actually panicking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...\Nit's just the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way this situation\Nis the same as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she getting mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to break it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this situation\Nis not the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BAM BAM\NCome sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have\Na strategy meeting right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BAM BAM\NWe're going to have\Na strategy meeting right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genos! You're Class S.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Association executives\Nhaven't told you about their next moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supporting\NMaster Saitama yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at a martial arts tournament\Nand also in a battle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention,\Nthe transmitter for the Association
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got melted and was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped mine\Ninto a crack in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed mine was broken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been because of the\Nshockwaves from Saitama's punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's our next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the brink of war\Nwith the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to undergo\Nsome repairs first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna need time to recover
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before we can\Nget back into action again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, King?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's some other business\NI have to tend to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Saitama and I are the only ones\Nwho are ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters probably\Nhas its own special task force
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's devising a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at times like this, actions\Ntaken by Class-B heroes and below
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can affect their future evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we should try to\Ndo something to contribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE\NAre you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the enemy is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a large group of monsters\Nthat usually act independently
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they have formed an alliance\Nwhich is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their organizational structure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,likely is more about domination\Nthan cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a boss giving orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, a monster group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Garou's joined up with them,\Nthat's gonna be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we may never get another\Nchance to fight Garou alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they still have any monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as strong as that centipede\Non their side
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well quit\Nbeing a hero, Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Hero Hunter\Nyou've been wanting to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was at that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my way home, I heard that\Nhe hunted down more heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since\Nhe hasn't come for me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm the Caped Baldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Saitama?\N- Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Garou is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I find Garou, I'll punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also buy\Nnapa cabbage on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I was calling the shots,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I'm left out in the cold again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to get Saitama{\i0}\N{\i1}and his crew{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to join the Blizzard Bunch{\i0}\N{\i1}will not be easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where am I?{\i0}\N{\i1}Did I survive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My memory is a bit fuzzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome to the Monster Association.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that you are reading this{\i0}\N{\i1}means you survived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be aware that we are the ones{\i0}\N{\i1}who saved your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So wait quietly in this room{\i0}\N{\i1}without causing any trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Going outside right now will only{\i0}\N{\i1}make you a target for heroes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What you need is a place to belong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a change of clothes.{\i0}\N{\i1}Please feel free to use them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oww... It hurts like hell!!{\i0}\N{\i1}My whole body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm thirsty. And I need food...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to replenish my blood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was fighting the old man,{\i0}\N{\i1}then that bird guy appeared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster Association...{\i0}\N{\i1}They get on my nerves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to the old man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was fighting that centipede...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well, who cares...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smell of blood permeates{\i0}\N{\i1}the stagnant air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Makes me wanna puke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's so quiet,{\i0}\N{\i1}my ears are ringing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I deep underground?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who cares...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have mercy!\NWe were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never defy you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noo, I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you took out\Ntwo of my soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let you\Nwalk out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your employer equipped you\Nwith powerful gear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd better fight till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here just loves turning anyone\Nwho resists into a plaything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr...\NIt's all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. If that freak robot\Nhadn't shown up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could've escaped to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the advertising worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad a capable\Nnew recruit came to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Machine God G5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NMACHINE GOD G5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NMACHINE GOD G5\NI was deployed by the organization\Nto aid the Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Organization"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get to this hideout\Nwithout getting lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk to your creator?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.\NIn any case, we welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,\Nwe have another arrival anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay hidden{\i0}\N{\i1}and wait a little longer, Garou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A voice directly in my head!{\i0}\N{\i1}Is it telepathy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having fought them myself,\NI can say that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their battle suits have\Nextremely high combat capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are highly valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they appear to be\Ncustomized for each individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no one else, let alone a monster,\Nwould be able to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we should let them\Nlive and use them as pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're mine.\NI'll train you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train?\NWhat on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! I'm lucky to\Nhave such promising slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garou. You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So that's the Hero Hunter.\N- He got rescued...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I like him.\N- ...and treated for his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Gyoro-Gyoro\Ntake interest in a mere human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is he human? A monster?\N- Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have an important talk\Nwith him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck is that giant{\i0}\N{\i1}in the back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the recent battle,\Nthere are fewer than 30 remaining
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,threat-level Demon or higher\Nmonsters left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so,\Nwe are still strong enough to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what we lack right now\Nis unity...and a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to become a member\Nof the leadership and assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A leader already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty sweet deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a strong anti-hero ideology\Nlike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a lone wolf,\Nbut even if he is battered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way he goes for the jugular\Nagainst Class-S heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is truly praiseworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, our boss, Lord Orochi,\Nhas one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prove that you are a true monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to grow a horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who it is.\NBring me the head of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a hero's life you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to give you the bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Silverfang and his buddies\Nare alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Centichoro was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.\NI have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NINSECT GOD\NHmph, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want so badly to hear\Na human scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NKING THE RIPPER\NI want so badly to hear\Na human scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NKING THE RIPPER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THREAT LEVEL: DEMON\NKING THE RIPPER\NI'm about to lose my mind.\NHurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garou went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, it was Goketsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And today, Centichoro was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet even Gyoro-Gyoro\Ndidn't expect two top monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go down\Nbefore the decisive battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why he's trying to recruit\Nthe Hero Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can be\None of the key warriors?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read Gyoro-Gyoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I'm interested\Nor anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can destroy\Nthe Hero Association and Flash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We recruited
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed-o'-Sound Sonic\Nbut what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he couldn't adapt\Nto the monster cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffered all night,\Nbut I think the worst is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate those bastards from\Nthe Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me my stomach\Nwould get this upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay 'em back for this one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had any intention of\Nteaming up with the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to\Ntake advantage of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only target is Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it...a new power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is definitely changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may take a while\Nto get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is monsterization?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not that it's anything special.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SONIC LOST TWO KILOGRAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:24:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER TRAITS

